    "It was the model to compete when it was introduced at the ILSVRC 2014 Conference.",
    "VGG-16, developed by the University of Oxford's Visual Graphics Group, outperformed AlexNet at the time and was quickly adopted by researchers and industry for image classification tasks Table IV.TABLE IV.",
